              code: `SELECT name, salary,\n  RANK()       OVER w AS rk,\n  DENSE_RANK() OVER w AS drk,\n  NTILE(4)     OVER w AS quartile,\n  LAG(salary)  OVER w AS prev_salary\nFROM employees\nWINDOW w AS (ORDER BY salary DESC);`,
              takeaway: 'Use NTILE for quick "split into deciles/quartiles" — saves you from manual percentile arithmetic.',
