              code: `db.events.createIndex({ user_id: 1, ts: -1 })\ndb.events.find({ user_id: U, ts: { $gte: t } })\n  .sort({ ts: -1 })\n  .explain("executionStats")\n// Look for "IXSCAN" not "COLLSCAN" in winningPlan`,
              takeaway: 'Always check `explain("executionStats")` after creating an index — without it, you\'re guessing whether it\'s used.',
