              code: `// Filter Action setup (UI):\n// Dashboard → Actions → Add Action → Filter\n//   Source: ChartA (Run on: Select)\n//   Target: ChartB\n//   Source field: Category → Target field: Category`,
              takeaway: 'Use containers + tiled layouts — they scale far better than free-floating placement when devices change size.',
